{"lemma":"صَنِيعُ","slug":"صَنِيعُ","root":"ص.ن.ع","root_slug":"ص-ن-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ن-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25016"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of صَنَعَ (ṣanaʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"action, act, deed"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"good deed, kind act"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of صَنَعَ (ṣanaʕa)."},"ipa":["/sˤa.niːʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25016","headword_ar":"صَنِيعٌ","root":"SnE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of 1 [q. v.]. (MA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSonuwEN","text_ar":"مَصْنُوعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Made, wrought, manufactured, fabricated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constructed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skilfully,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 1, first sentence]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  [Hence,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Food"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared, and to which people are invited;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSonaEapN","text_ar":"مَصْنَعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [the same, i. e.] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a repast, feast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"banquet, to which friends are invited:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kunotu fiY SaniyEi fulaAnK","text_ar":"كُنْتُ فِى صَنِيعِ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I was at the repast of such a one, made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared, by him, to which people were invited:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaSonaEapi","text_ar":"المَصْنَعَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the repast to which friends were invited."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And (i. e. the former word) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Food prepared to be dispensed in the way,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cause, of God."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  Also, applied to a sword,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Polished,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and proved by experience;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so applied to an arrow: (K, TA:) or, applied to a sword,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frequently renovated by polishing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SunuEN","text_ar":"صُنُعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b5-  And, applied to a horse, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Well tended;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"supplied with fodder, and fattened."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And [in like manner it is applied to a human being:] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa SaniyEiY","text_ar":"هُوَ صَنِيعِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is the person whom I have reared;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whom I have educated, disciplined,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trained, well;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaniyEatiY","text_ar":"صَنِيعَتِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, * O, K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnK","text_ar":"فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa muSoTanaEapu","text_ar":"هُوَ مُصْطَنَعَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he is the person whom such a one has reared;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (Z, TA.) ―         -b6-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A goodly and clean garment."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L, TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A deed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an action;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, KL;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaniyEapN","text_ar":"صَنِيعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ham p. 198:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaEa","text_ar":"صَنَعَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi SaniyEFA qabiyHFA","text_ar":"بِهِ صَنِيعًا قَبِيحًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did to him an evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a foul, deed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwo'u SaniyEapK","text_ar":"سُوْءُ صَنِيعَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The evil"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consequence"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a deed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham ubi suprà.) And [particularly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A good deed, a benefit, favour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind act;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaniyEapN","text_ar":"صَنِيعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, * O, Msb, K:) [see a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSonaEN","text_ar":"مَصْنَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] pl. [of either, of the latter agreeably with rule,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaAy^iEu","text_ar":"صَنَايِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Skilful in work"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the hands or hand: (S, O, K, TA:) fem. [in this sense] with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaEN","text_ar":"صَنَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places. Accord. to IDrst, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaniEN","text_ar":"صَنِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[likewise] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Skilled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skilful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaniEa","text_ar":"صَنِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but IB says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaniEa","text_ar":"صَنِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has not been heard. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K","TA","S","A"]}]}}